{"tid":2238178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因零用錢起爭執　少年2分鐘內掌摑媽媽5巴掌　母：你這樣對我？","createTime":"2020-10-11T02:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T11:04:03.000Z","uid":202966,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c3f114bbeeebb0b0a22fe2a47bf5b423d5025f","tid":2238178,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224297106051072.jpeg/c_b0R3yFjBVJyw-vgVSQqQM2VbESDZq1oZPvgKGT74A?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224297106051072.jpeg%2Fc_b0R3yFjBVJyw-vgVSQqQM2VbESDZq1oZPvgKGT74A%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=fb5e097d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家家有本難念的經，但無論如何都不應對家人動粗。近日新加坡一段TikTok影片在網絡上瘋傳，只見一名火爆男生與坐在地上的媽媽爭執，男生2分鐘內5次掌摑她，爭執內容疑似和零用錢及整理家具有關。事件愈演愈烈，當地警方介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n據當地傳媒報道，事件發生於上月29日，閉路電視片段最先被傳至TikTok，其後被轉載至facebook等社交網站。從影片可見，該名媽媽坐在地上組裝家具，男生當時向她討錢，媽媽則回應「已給了你10塊（約57港元），我也無能為力」，男生其後再追問下月有多少零用錢，媽媽回覆「100塊（約560港元）」，但他顯然不太滿意，遂用手掌打媽媽的頭。<br />\n<br />\n其後，兩人再為組裝家具起爭執，男生竟突然摑了媽媽兩巴掌，第3巴掌打過去時，媽媽又大喊「你就打我啊！」，男生聽見後還真的再補了兩巴，並訓斥道「我跟你說過多少次！」，在影片結束前，媽媽語帶硬咽地問：「你這樣對媽媽嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n影片上傳網絡上即引起公憤，網民紛紛批評男生不孝，又指對媽媽怎可以如此不尊重，但亦有人認為其母的教育方法有問題，不應任由兒子對自己「打不還手、罵不還口」。有網民看不過眼而報警，警方證實接到報案，正進行調查，而男生就讀的學校校長回答傳媒查詢稱，由於警方調查進行中，不便置評。<br />\n男生事後亦在Instagram解釋稱，當時跟媽媽要的100元（約560港元）是他的零用錢，到家後有好好跟她說，但媽媽卻對他大喊，但他亦為自己的行為道歉，又指已和媽媽談過此事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224521081884672.png/nlFzQzHX-DQkCrwKV47OphNdErMGmv6S0toYDtLaGA4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224521081884672.png%2FnlFzQzHX-DQkCrwKV47OphNdErMGmv6S0toYDtLaGA4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7619b648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224524076617728.png/KBdq9dO5qNsqx9Oz8gCixKHrG9P2WarRV85woVfOcKE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224524076617728.png%2FKBdq9dO5qNsqx9Oz8gCixKHrG9P2WarRV85woVfOcKE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fb909da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224526580617216.png/0fcDvBLnn36bccQMisRhohhRbD2cCRK0ovxGoaL8RqE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224526580617216.png%2F0fcDvBLnn36bccQMisRhohhRbD2cCRK0ovxGoaL8RqE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=681087b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224528988147712.png/DgZFKlgwkxiMDNI0gvqH6UwPtkPY5_aXxpRWJ8aUVic?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224528988147712.png%2FDgZFKlgwkxiMDNI0gvqH6UwPtkPY5_aXxpRWJ8aUVic%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d188b51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224531303403521.png/L8kV7qDpASs_FjVisBKxau4ms7BbJG_753LPC-dyzws?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224531303403521.png%2FL8kV7qDpASs_FjVisBKxau4ms7BbJG_753LPC-dyzws%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fc62bf6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201009/391224533517996033.png/4mYgAxsuyWukIt5n75MK5CpOa_mp9X14_PFGLvzxRi4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201009%2F391224533517996033.png%2F4mYgAxsuyWukIt5n75MK5CpOa_mp9X14_PFGLvzxRi4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=50020128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85403795aa8ce1b751865dfb5ee276ebeb6e9acb","tid":2238178,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"三巴姐<br />\n最後兩巴自己要求"},{"pid":"63368be8778a00b27082ffe15bd81aca73c87123","tid":2238178,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街<img src=\"/assets/fa